snippet.title: Drunk Prime Minister (Kamla Persad Bissessar)

localized.description: The prime minister of the Republic of Trinidad and Tobago appears drunk on stage thinking she has won the local government elections in the country when in fact she and her government lost. She first taught she got six seats but it turned out to be five. PNM had won the elections with 8 seats to 5 with one seat tied. She sings at first. Seems she had a little too much to drink. Perhaps a few shots of Puncheon, a Trinidad rum. Enjoy!
